data.description: Welcome to your rural retreat in Marion! This three bedroom, two bath home sits at the dead end of Bing Lane tucked back on 4.08 acres! Step into cozy charm as you're greeted by a combo living and dining room area complete with a crackling wood-burning fireplace. The cathedral ceilings draw your eye to the beautiful woodworking of the home. The airy kitchen offers direct access to the back deck for  take in the surrounding nature. Watch the deer, turkey, other wildlife right off the deck! With two bedrooms downstairs, an additional bedroom upstairs, plus a versatile loft, there's ample space for all your needs. The loft could easily make a fourth bedroom. Speaking of views, enjoy a picturesque panorama of the neighboring horses from every window. Connected off the living room is a handy mudroom ready to store your outdoor gear. Plus, you can embrace your inner homesteader with a lean-to chicken coop and garden boxes. New carpet was installed in most of the downstairs. The shade trees ensure low electric bills in the summer. This home gives you the freedom to transform this expansive property into your personal paradise. Whether you crave a peaceful oasis or an outdoor enthusiast's playground, the possibilities are endless. Call today for a showing!
